<text><body>
<lb n="0070c05"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"></milestone>
<lb n="0070c06"/>
<lb n="0070c07"/><head type="no">No. 332 [Nos. 310(29), 333]</head>
<lb n="0070c08"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="1" type="卷"></mulu><jhead>佛說優填王經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0070c09"/>
<lb n="0070c10"/><byline type="Translator">西晉<note n="0070003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔沙門〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0070003"><lem>沙門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>釋法炬<note n="0070004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔奉詔〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔奉詔〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070004"><lem>奉　詔</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0070c11"/><div1 type="jing"><p>聞如是。一時佛在拘深國。<note n="0070005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（國）＋王【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（國）＋王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070005"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">國王</rdg></app>號曰優填。拘
<lb n="0070c12"/>深國有逝心。名摩<note n="0070006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">回＝因【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070006"><lem>回</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">因</rdg></app>提。生女端正華色世間
<lb n="0070c13"/>少雙。父&CB00418;女容一國希有。名曰無比。鄰國諸
<lb n="0070c14"/>王。群<note n="0070007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">僚＝寮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">僚＝寮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070007"><lem>僚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">寮</rdg></app>豪姓靡不娉焉。父答曰。若有君子
<lb n="0070c15"/>容與女齊吾其應之。佛時行在其國。逝心。
<lb n="0070c16"/>&CB00418;佛三十二相八十種好。身色紫金巍巍堂
<lb n="0070c17"/>堂光儀無上。心喜而曰。吾女獲匹。歸語其妻
<lb n="0070c18"/>曰。吾為無比得婿。促莊飾女將往也。夫妻
<lb n="0070c19"/>共服飾。其女步<note n="0070008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瑤＝搖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瑤＝搖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070008"><lem>瑤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">搖</rdg></app>華光。珠璣瓔珞莊<note n="0070009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚴＝飾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚴＝飾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070009"><lem>嚴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飾</rdg></app>光
<lb n="0070c20"/>國。夫妻共將女至佛所。妻道見佛&CB00528;相好之
<lb n="0070c21"/>文光<note n="0070010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彩＝綵【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0070010"><lem>彩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">綵</rdg></app>之色。非世所有。知為天尊。謂其夫
<lb n="0070c22"/>曰。此人足跡文理乃爾。非世所聞斯將非凡。
<lb n="0070c23"/>必自清淨無復婬欲。將不取吾女無自辱也。
<lb n="0070c24"/>夫曰。何以知其然。妻因說偈言。</p>
<lb n="0070c25"/><lg><l>婬人曳踵行</l><l>恚者<note n="0070011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">操＝歛【元】【明】</note><app n="0070011"><lem>操</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">歛</rdg></app>指步</l>
<lb n="0070c26"/><l>愚者足<note n="0070012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">躘＝蹴【元】【明】</note><app n="0070012"><lem>躘</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">蹴</rdg></app>地</l><l>斯跡天人尊</l></lg>
<lb n="0070c27"/><p>逝心曰。非爾女人所知。汝不樂者<note n="0070013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＋（自）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＋（自）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070013"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">便自</rdg></app>還歸。
<lb n="0070c28"/>乃自將女<note n="0070014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（往）＋詣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（往）＋詣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070014"><lem>詣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">往詣</rdg></app>佛所。稽首佛足白佛言。大人
<lb n="0070c29"/>勤勞教授。身無供養有是&CB00308;女願給箕&CB00416;。佛
<pb n="0071a" id="T12.0332.0071a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0071a01"/>言。汝以女為好耶。答曰。生得此女顏容實
<lb n="0071a02"/>好世間無雙。諸國王豪姓多有求者不以應
<lb n="0071a03"/>之。竊見大人光色巍巍非世所見。貪得供養
<lb n="0071a04"/>故宜自歸耳。佛言。此女之好為著何許。逝心
<lb n="0071a05"/>曰。從頭至足周遍觀之無不好也。佛言。惑哉
<lb n="0071a06"/>肉眼。吾觀之從頭至足無一好耶。若頭上有
<lb n="0071a07"/>髮。但是毛象馬之尾亦皆爾也。髮下有髑髏。
<lb n="0071a08"/>但是骨屠家&CB00337;頭骨亦爾也。頭中有腦者如
<lb n="0071a09"/>泥<note n="0071001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02312;＝腥【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0071001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02312;＝腥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0071001"><lem>&CB02312;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">腥</rdg></app>臊<note n="0071002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">送＝逆【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">送＝逆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071002"><lem>送</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">逆</rdg></app>。鼻下之著地莫能蹈者。目者是
<lb n="0071a10"/><note n="0071003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">脆＝胞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">脆＝胞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071003"><lem>脆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">胞</rdg></app>決之純汁。鼻中有涕。口但有唾。腹藏肝
<lb n="0071a11"/>肺皆亦<app type="＊" source="0071001"><lem>&CB02312;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腥</rdg></app>臊。腸胃膀胱但成屎尿腐臭難論。
<lb n="0071a12"/>腹為<note n="0071004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">幃＝韋【元】【明】</note><app n="0071004"><lem>幃</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">韋</rdg></app>囊裹諸不淨四支手足骨骨相<note n="0071005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝柱【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0071005"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">柱</rdg></app>筋
<lb n="0071a13"/>連皮&CB02305;。但恃氣息以動作之。譬若木人機關
<lb n="0071a14"/>作之。既畢解<note n="0071006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">列＝剝【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">列＝剝【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071006"><lem>列</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">剝</rdg></app>其體節節。相離手足狼<note n="0071007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">藉＝籍【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0071007"><lem>藉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">籍</rdg></app>
<lb n="0071a15"/>人亦如是。有何等好而云少雙。昔者吾在貝
<lb n="0071a16"/>多樹下。第六魔天王莊飾三女。顏容華色天
<lb n="0071a17"/>中無比非徒此<note n="0071008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">論＝倫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">論＝倫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071008"><lem>論</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">倫</rdg></app>。欲以壞吾道意。我為說
<lb n="0071a18"/>身中穢惡。即皆化成老母形壞不復慚愧而
<lb n="0071a19"/>去。今是屎囊欲何所戀急將還去。吾不取也。
<lb n="0071a20"/>逝心聞佛所說忽然慚恥無辭復言。又白佛
<lb n="0071a21"/>言。若仁不取者更以妻優填王可乎不。佛不
<lb n="0071a22"/>答焉。逝心。即送女與優填王。王獲女大悅。拜
<lb n="0071a23"/>父為太傅。為女<note n="0071009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">興＝與【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">興＝與【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071009"><lem>興</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">與</rdg></app>宮。伎樂千人以給侍之。
<lb n="0071a24"/>王正后師事佛。得須陀洹道。此女讚之於王。
<lb n="0071a25"/>王惑其言以百箭射其后。后見箭不懼都無
<lb n="0071a26"/>恚怒。一意念佛慈心長跪向王。箭皆繞后
<lb n="0071a27"/>三匝還住王前。百箭皆爾。王乃自驚<note n="0071010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">暢＝悵【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">暢＝悵【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071010"><lem>暢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悵</rdg></app>然
<lb n="0071a28"/>而懼。即駕白<note n="0071011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">象＝像【宮】</note><app n="0071011"><lem>象</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">像</rdg></app>金車馳詣佛所。未到下車
<lb n="0071a29"/><note n="0071012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">避＝僻【宋】【宮】，辟【元】【明】</note><note n="0071012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">避＝僻【宋】【宮】，＝辟【元】【明】</note><app n="0071012"><lem>避</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">僻</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">辟</rdg></app><note n="0071013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝徒【宮】</note><app n="0071013"><lem>從</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">徒</rdg></app>步進稽首佛足。長跪自陳曰。吾有重
<pb n="0071b" id="T12.0332.0071b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0071b01"/>咎在三尊。所以彼婬妖<note n="0071014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝縱【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071014"><lem>從</lem><rdg wit="【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">縱</rdg></app>欲興邪。於佛聖
<lb n="0071b02"/>眾每一惡念。以箭百<note n="0071015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枚＝放【宮】</note><app n="0071015"><lem>枚</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">放</rdg></app>射佛弟子。如事陳
<lb n="0071b03"/>之&CB00418;之心懼。<note n="0071016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【宮】＊</note><app n="0071016"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>佛至真無量之慈。白衣弟
<lb n="0071b04"/>子慈力乃爾。豈況無上正真佛乎。我今首過
<lb n="0071b05"/>歸命三尊。<app type="＊" source="0071016"><lem>唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">惟</rdg></app>佛弘慈原赦其咎。佛笑曰。
<lb n="0071b06"/>善哉王。覺惡悔過此明人行也。吾受王善意。
<lb n="0071b07"/>王稽首。如是至三佛亦三受之。王又頭面著
<lb n="0071b08"/>地退就坐曰。稟氣<note n="0071017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">匈＝凶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">匈＝凶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071017"><lem>匈</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">凶</rdg></app>頑忿戾自恣無忍辱心。
<lb n="0071b09"/>三毒不除惡行快意。順女妖邪不知其惡。自
<lb n="0071b10"/>惟壽終必入地獄。願佛加哀廣說女惡魑魅
<lb n="0071b11"/>之態。入其羅網&CB00458;能自拔。吾聞其禍必以
<lb n="0071b12"/>自<note n="0071018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誡＝戒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誡＝戒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071018"><lem>誡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">戒</rdg></app>。國民巨細得以改操。佛言。用此<note n="0071019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">問為且＝為問且【宋】【元】，為問具【明】</note><note n="0071019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">問為且＝為問且【宋】【元】，＝為問具【明】</note><app n="0071019"><lem>問
<lb n="0071b13"/>為且</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">為問且</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">為問具</rdg></app>說餘義。王曰。餘事異日說之不<note n="0071020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">晚＝免【宮】</note><app n="0071020"><lem>晚</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">免</rdg></app>。女
<lb n="0071b14"/>亂惑意<note n="0071021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兇＝凶【宮】</note><app n="0071021"><lem>兇</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">凶</rdg></app>禍之大。不聞其禍何緣遠之。願
<lb n="0071b15"/>佛具為吾釋地獄之變及女人之穢。佛言。具
<lb n="0071b16"/>聽。男子有<note n="0071022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淫＝媱【三】【宮】下同</note><note n="0071022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淫＝媱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0071022"><lem>淫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">媱</rdg></app>之惡&CB00230;&CB00418;女妖。王曰。善願受
<lb n="0071b17"/>明教。佛言。具聽男子有四惡急所。當知世有
<lb n="0071b18"/>婬夫。&M010527;想&CB00418;女思聞妖聲。遠捨正法疑真信
<lb n="0071b19"/>邪。<note n="0071023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬＝邪【宮】</note><app n="0071023"><lem>婬</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">邪</rdg></app>網所<note n="0071024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02280;＝纏【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02280;＝纏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071024"><lem>&CB02280;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">纏</rdg></app>沒在盲冥。為欲所使如奴畏
<lb n="0071b20"/>主。貪樂女色不覺九孔惡露之臭穢。渾沌欲
<lb n="0071b21"/>中。如&CB00337;處溷不覺其臭。快以為安不計後當
<lb n="0071b22"/>在無<note n="0071025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">澤＝擇【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">澤＝擇【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071025"><lem>澤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">擇</rdg></app>之獄受痛無極。注心在淫<note n="0071026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">噉＝&CB00105;【宋】【宮】，泆【元】【明】</note><note n="0071026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">噉＝&CB00105;【宋】【宮】，＝泆【元】【明】</note><app n="0071026"><lem>噉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB00105;</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">泆</rdg></app>其涕
<lb n="0071b23"/>唾翫其膿血。珍之如玉甘之如蜜。故曰欲態
<lb n="0071b24"/>之士此為一惡態也。又親之養子懷妊生育。
<lb n="0071b25"/>稚得長大勤苦難論。到子成人<note n="0071027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB06096;＝擢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071027" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">懼</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB06096;</rdg></app>＝擢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071027"><lem>懼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">擢</rdg></app>家竭財膝
<lb n="0071b26"/>行肘步。因媒表情致彼為妻。若在異域尋而
<lb n="0071b27"/>追之。不問遠近不避勤苦。注意在婬捐忘親
<lb n="0071b28"/>老。既得為妻貴之如寶。欲私相娛樂惡見父
<lb n="0071b29"/>母。信其妖言。或致&CB00508;訟不惟身所從生。<note n="0071028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">孤＝辜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">孤＝辜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071028"><lem>孤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">辜</rdg></app>
<pb n="0071c" id="T12.0332.0071c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0071c01"/>親無量之恩。斯謂二惡態也。又人處世勤
<lb n="0071c02"/>苦疲勞。躬自致財本<note n="0071029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝有【宮】</note><app n="0071029"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">有</rdg></app>誠信敬道之意尊戴
<lb n="0071c03"/>沙門。梵志之心覺世非常。布施為福取妻之
<lb n="0071c04"/>後。情惑婬欲愚蔽自擁。背真向邪專由女
<lb n="0071c05"/><note n="0071030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">色＝衒【宮】</note><app n="0071030"><lem>色</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">衒</rdg></app>。若有布施之意。雖欲發言相呼女色。
<lb n="0071c06"/>絕清淨行更成小人。不識佛經之<note n="0071031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戒＝重誡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">戒＝重誡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071031"><lem>戒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">重誡</rdg></app>禍福之
<lb n="0071c07"/>歸。苟為婬色投身羅網。必墮惡道終而不改。
<lb n="0071c08"/>斯謂三惡態也。又為人子不惟養恩。治生致
<lb n="0071c09"/>財不以養親。但以東西廣求婬路。懷持寶物
<lb n="0071c10"/>招人婦女。或殺六畜婬祀鬼神。飲酒歌舞合
<lb n="0071c11"/>會之後。<note n="0071032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至＝亙【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至＝亙【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071032"><lem>至</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">亙</rdg></app>求方便更相招呼。以遂<note n="0071033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奸＝姦【宮】</note><app n="0071033"><lem>奸</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">姦</rdg></app>情。
<lb n="0071c12"/>及其獲偶。喜無以喻。婬結縛著無所復識當
<lb n="0071c13"/>爾之時<app type="＊" source="0071016"><lem>唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">惟</rdg></app>此為樂。不覺惡露之臭穢地獄之
<lb n="0071c14"/>苦痛。一則可笑二則可畏。譬若狂<note n="0071034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">犬＝笑【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">犬＝笑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071034"><lem>犬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">笑</rdg></app>不知
<lb n="0071c15"/>其非。斯謂四惡態也。佛言。男子有是四惡用
<lb n="0071c16"/>墮三塗。當審遠此<note n="0071035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">態＝能【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">態＝能【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071035"><lem>態</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">能</rdg></app>免苦耳。復聽說女人之
<lb n="0071c17"/>惡。佛便說偈言。</p>
<lb n="0071c18"/><lg><l>已為欲所使</l><l>放意不能安</l>
<lb n="0071c19"/><l>習施於非法</l><l>將何以為賢</l>
<lb n="0071c20"/><l>欲為畜生行</l><l>以<note n="0071036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝為【明】</note><app n="0071036"><lem>欲</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">為</rdg></app>還自殃</l>
<lb n="0071c21"/><l>溷虫在臭中</l><l>不知為處難</l>
<lb n="0071c22"/><l>如虫在冥中</l><l>不知東以西</l>
<lb n="0071c23"/><l>結著於婬欲</l><l>惡此亦虫論</l>
<lb n="0071c24"/><l>婬既不見道</l><l>日夜種罪根</l>
<lb n="0071c25"/><l>現世君臣亂</l><l>上下為迷昏</l>
<lb n="0071c26"/><l>王法為錯亂</l><l>正法為迷<note n="0071037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">樊＝焚【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071037"><lem>樊</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">焚</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0071c27"/><l>農夫捨常業</l><l>賈人為<note n="0071038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">珍＝彌【宮】</note><app n="0071038"><lem>珍</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">彌</rdg></app>連</l>
<lb n="0071c28"/><l>現世更牢獄</l><l>死復入太山</l>
<lb n="0071c29"/><l>當受百種毒</l><l>其痛難可<note n="0071039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝言【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071039"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">言</rdg></app></l>
<pb n="0072a" id="T12.0332.0072a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0072a01"/><l>洋銅灌其口</l><l>山<note n="0072001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">連＝車【元】【明】</note><app n="0072001"><lem>連</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">車</rdg></app>笮其身</l>
<lb n="0072a02"/><l>此輩有百數</l><l>難可一一陳</l>
<lb n="0072a03"/><l>常在三惡道</l><l>宛轉如車輪</l>
<lb n="0072a04"/><l>若世時有佛</l><l>而已不得聞</l>
<lb n="0072a05"/><l>女人最為惡</l><l>難與為因緣</l>
<lb n="0072a06"/><l>恩愛一縛著</l><l>牽人入罪門</l>
<lb n="0072a07"/><l>女人<note n="0072002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為何＝何為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為何＝何為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072002"><lem>為何</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">何為</rdg></app>好</l><l>但是屎尿囊</l>
<lb n="0072a08"/><l>何不諦係視</l><l>為此而狂荒</l>
<lb n="0072a09"/><l>其內甚臭穢</l><l>外為嚴飾容</l>
<lb n="0072a10"/><l>家有含毒蝎</l><l>劇如蛇以龍</l>
<lb n="0072a11"/><l>譬<note n="0072003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝若【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如＝若【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072003"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">若</rdg></app>錦韜<note n="0072004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">牟＝矛【元】【明】</note><app n="0072004"><lem>牟</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">矛</rdg></app></l><l>羅縠<note n="0072005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02280;＝&M034294;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02280;＝&M034294;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072005"><lem>&CB02280;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&M034294;</rdg></app>鋒鋩</l>
<lb n="0072a12"/><l>愚者&CB00418;其表</l><l>翫之以自殃</l>
<lb n="0072a13"/><l>智者覺而捨</l><l>癡者致死傷</l>
<lb n="0072a14"/><l>婬欲亦如是</l><l>抱刃以自喪</l>
<lb n="0072a15"/><l>&CB00418;新即厭故</l><l>所樂亦無常</l>
<lb n="0072a16"/><l>言為刀斧截</l><l>笑為<note n="0072006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">棘以荊＝荊以棘【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">棘以荊＝荊以棘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072006"><lem>棘以荊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">荊以棘</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0072a17"/><l>內懷臭穢毒</l><l>飾外以華香</l>
<lb n="0072a18"/><l>癡人貪其味</l><l>不惟後受殃</l>
<lb n="0072a19"/><l>譬<note n="0072007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝如【明】</note><app n="0072007"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app><note n="0072008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鴆＝沈【宮】</note><app n="0072008"><lem>鴆</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">沈</rdg></app>毒藥</l><l>以和甘露漿</l>
<lb n="0072a20"/><l>所向無不壞</l><l>飲之皆仆僵</l>
<lb n="0072a21"/><l>亦如薪得火</l><l>草木被重霜</l>
<lb n="0072a22"/><l>&CB00418;表不計&M034294;</l><l>是為最非<note n="0072009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">詳＝祥【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">詳＝祥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072009"><lem>詳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">祥</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0072a23"/><l>女毒甚於是</l><l>草乃見形傷</l>
<lb n="0072a24"/><l>絕欲以求道</l><l>故有婬欲情</l>
<lb n="0072a25"/><l>其形甚易見</l><l>癡人情不絕</l>
<lb n="0072a26"/><l>羅網四面張</l><l>去道如絲髮</l>
<lb n="0072a27"/><l>人本清淨種</l><l>如魚處深淵</l>
<lb n="0072a28"/><l>智者乃自覺</l><l>著網不得還</l>
<lb n="0072a29"/><l>欲網甚於是</l><l>結縛甚欲堅</l>
<pb n="0072b" id="T12.0332.0072b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0072b01"/><l>投身<note n="0072010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">置＝&CB00155;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">置＝&CB00155;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072010"><lem>置</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB00155;</rdg></app>荊棘</l><l>可得脫其身</l>
<lb n="0072b02"/><l>譬若飢猿猴</l><l>望見熟甘果</l>
<lb n="0072b03"/><l>專心投色欲</l><l>是輩百向墮</l>
<lb n="0072b04"/><l>亦如魚食鉤</l><l>飛蛾入燈火</l>
<lb n="0072b05"/><l>愚者見歡喜</l><l>不<note n="0072011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝遣【宋】</note><app n="0072011"><lem>惟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">遣</rdg></app>後受禍</l></lg>
<lb n="0072b06"/><p>佛說如是。優填王歡喜即以頭面著地。白佛
<lb n="0072b07"/>言。實從生<note n="0072012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072012"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>來不聞女人之惡乃爾。男子。
<lb n="0072b08"/><note n="0072013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悖＝勃【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悖＝勃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072013"><lem>悖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">勃</rdg></app>亂隨之墮罪。但不知故不<note n="0072014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">制＝斷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">制＝斷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072014"><lem>制</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">斷</rdg></app>心意從今
<lb n="0072b09"/>已後終身自悔。歸命三尊不敢復犯。為佛作
<lb n="0072b10"/>禮歡喜而去。</p></div1>
<lb n="0072b11"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說優填王經</jhead></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>